{
  "stem": "7282.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was still seeing battles on the Warsaw-- on the Wisla, or what.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And since then, they start to run.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They start to run.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in, in Germany, I came over in [NON-ENGLISH]-- Liegnitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There it was our company.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I'd been there since '45, at that time in, in, in, in Liegnitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then, when the wars ended, they started to mobilize the people from the army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "First went my brother-in-law, like, here, here-- brother-in-law, the older sister's husband.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He came first because he is much older than me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I still was in, in the army till 1946.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was in the army.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my wife, at that time, I, I, I had contact with her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I knew where she is because I had the address.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But they took her on the working-- in the labor camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they both live in the same place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I got the address.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so my nephew was still there, what.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I had contact with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I knew where, where she was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then I received a letter from her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And she said she's leaving this place, and she's going to Kiev.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "This was, like-- it was in an orphanage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And she was working there as a teacher in the orphanage.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And after the war, the parents [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] asked them to bring the kids back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was, like, the president from the orphanage, it was a friend of hers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They lived very good together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she says, listen, if you-- if you want to get out from here, you better come with me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She thought it's a good idea because her sisters already left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, her sister still was there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
